"{\"uid\": \"jamaica-gleaner.com-article-entertainment-20240726-celine-dion-makes-musical-comeback-paris-olympics-eiffel-tower\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS (AP) - Celine Dion made a triumphant return Friday with a very public performance: closing out the Paris Olympics' opening ceremony from the Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 9, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999991315391205, \"rank\": 8.589983355815547e-07, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PARIS\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 5}, {\"ngram\": \"Celine Dion\", \"from\": 13, \"to\": 24}, {\"ngram\": \"a triumphant return\", \"from\": 30, \"to\": 49}, {\"ngram\": \"a very public performance\", \"from\": 62, \"to\": 87}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics' opening ceremony\", \"from\": 101, \"to\": 137}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 143, \"to\": 159}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nearly two years after revealing her stiff person syndrome diagnosis, Dion belted Edith Piaf's \\\"Hymne \\u00e0 l'amour\\\" (\\\"Hymn to Love\\\") as the finale of the roughly four-hour spectacle.\", \"from\": 162, \"to\": 341, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her stiff person syndrome diagnosis\", \"from\": 195, \"to\": 230}, {\"ngram\": \"Dion\", \"from\": 232, \"to\": 236}, {\"ngram\": \"Edith Piaf's \\\"Hymne \\u00e0 l'amour\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 273}, {\"ngram\": \"(\\\"Hymn to Love\", \"from\": 275, \"to\": 289}, {\"ngram\": \"the finale\", \"from\": 295, \"to\": 305}, {\"ngram\": \"the roughly four-hour spectacle\", \"from\": 309, \"to\": 340}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her appearance had been teased for weeks, but organisers and Dion's representatives had refused to confirm whether she was performing.\", \"from\": 343, \"